The most significant technology move announced is the integration of BlackRock's Aladdin Wealth platform into EFG's advisory platform (November 2025). This gives CROs and Investment Counsellors access to advanced portfolio analytics, scenario modelling, risk insights, and proposal generation tools. This is the investment management intelligence layer.

**What Aladdin Wealth does not cover:**
- AI-automated workflow tools (meeting prep, note generation, client summaries)
- KYC and onboarding automation
- Agentic AI for back and middle office
- Data harmonisation across acquired entities
