No publicly named enterprise data platform. EFG's data architecture is fragmented — multiple booking centres, multiple acquired entities, and a history of cherry-picking peripheral applications from acquired banks. The 2023 core banking upgrade improved the transactional data layer but did not solve the client data harmonisation problem across jurisdictions.

