### Cloud
No public cloud strategy statement. The 2023 core banking upgrade and legacy decommissioning suggests some modernisation toward cloud-compatible infrastructure, but EFG has not made public statements about a cloud-first or hybrid cloud position comparable to its competitors.

### Compliance / AML / KYC
No named vendor publicly disclosed. EFG's Pillar 3 disclosures reference group compliance functions covering AML, KYC, sanctions screening, and cross-border activity monitoring. These are currently largely manual or semi-automated processes — a known operational bottleneck.

